Show HN: Postanza.ai – Infinite ideas for your B2B social media channels
text:
As a founder of several businesses and former owner of a digital marketing agency, I understand the struggle of coming up with fresh and engaging content ideas for social media. Especially when the recommended best practice is to post daily to keep your audience engaged.

So, I reached out to the Reddit community for some tips on what type of content they post and how they create their monthly content calendars. Based on their feedback, I developed an idea generator module that can provide you with endless content ideas for your social media channels.

I would love for you all to give it a try and let me know what you think!
